{
  "stem": "26142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he will take us to the Dniester River and will ferry us over across the Dniester.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said that he-- when he ferries you over-- he told us-- when he ferries you over, you-- you have to go a few hundred steps up-- up the hill.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then you make a left turn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then you hit-- you hit the highway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when you are on that highway, you go left until you see three white buildings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The three white buildings is-- is-- a grain dealer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One building is a grain storage, and the other one-- in one, is his house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You will see a lantern burning on the table-- on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You knock at the door, and they will let you in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you will be on the other side of the Dniester River.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now this was, again, against what we were supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, the Hungarians said they'll shoot us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, we managed to get-- it was already dark-- we managed to get back on foot to that widow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When we came, back we found our sister-in-law in hysterics, crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She got terribly scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We left in the morning for-- for a-- an hour or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And here we were detained the whole day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They thought-- and-- and-- and-- and it was-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we told-- we told her what-- what-- happened and what is going to-- to-- to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This Isaak Zummer told us also, he said, you are going to be over on the other side in this man's house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and-- and for-- for-- I regret very much that I don't remember their names-- the-- the grain dealer's name.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "From there, they will-- they will get you to a city called Horodenka.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
